<i>¶ You've got to shake it up</i>
<i>Wake it up ¶</i>

21:45.271 --> 21:47.738
¶ Rattle them skeleton bones

21:49.608 --> 21:52.810
Mateys, thanks for helping
teach Captain Hook the steps

21:52.812 --> 21:55.646
he needed to win
that prize rose.

21:55.648 --> 21:57.682
Let's count our gold doubloons

21:57.684 --> 21:59.984
and put them in our
Team Treasure Chest.

