[Jake] One, two, three...

22:25.144 --> 22:27.712
[Izzy] Four, five, six...

22:27.714 --> 22:30.681
[Cubby] Seven, eight, nine!

22:30.683 --> 22:33.684
[Jake] Yo-ho! For solving
pirate problems today,

22:33.686 --> 22:36.187
we got nine gold doubloons.

22:37.289 --> 22:39.457
Let's keep on dancing!

22:39.459 --> 22:40.624
Hit it, Skully!

22:40.626 --> 22:42.660
[up-tempo music plays]

22:42.662 --> 22:45.062
<i>¶ You've got to shake it up</i>
<i>and wake it up ¶</i>

22:45.064 --> 22:47.465
<i>¶ And rattle them</i>
<i>skeleton bones ¶</i>

22:47.467 --> 22:50.234
What a wonderful time!

22:50.236 --> 22:53.738
I could have danced all night.

22:53.740 --> 22:55.740
- [screams]
- [splashing]

22:55.742 --> 22:58.342
Smee! Sharky! Bones!

22:58.344 --> 23:01.045
[sputters] Save me!

23:01.047 --> 23:04.648
